description:
Gray Area Festival 2019 
http://grayareafestival.io/
Gray Area Festival is San Francisco's premier annual festival advancing culture and common good through the lens of art and technology.

Sarah Brin
http://sarahbrin.com
Sarah Brin is an art historian and creative producer who specializes in previously unanticipated situations involving technology, the public, and organizational change/infrastructure. 
She cares about building just, sustainable and inviting things. Sarah currently works as Strategic Partnerships Manager for Meow Wolf in Santa Fe, New Mexico.
